24
00:03:56,958 --> 00:03:58,625
AT AN INCREDIBLE PACE.

25
00:03:58,708 --> 00:04:01,500
IT'S SO BEAUTIFUL.

26
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:10,166
- Man: What the late
Dr. Stingray invented

27
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:12,333
