than just a robot.

28
00:04:12,416 --> 00:04:13,833
The Boomers being sold by Genom

29
00:04:13,916 --> 00:04:16,708
were only intended as shells
for his real creation--

30
00:04:16,791 --> 00:04:18,875
a new form
of artificial intelligence

31
00:04:18,958 --> 00:04:21,333
seeded within
the bio-organic metal

32
00:04:21,416 --> 00:04:23,875
that forms the basis
of a Boomer's power core.

33
00:04:23,958 --> 00:04:26,375
This organism grew
from a device implanted

34
00:04:26,458 --> 00:04:28,875
in the hypothalamus
of a test subject,

35
00:04:28,958 --> 00:04:30,958
duplicating
first her mental patterns

36
00:04:31,041 --> 00:04:33,791
and later a duplicate
of her body as well.

37
00:04:33,875 --> 00:04:35,833
It is this ability
that appears to be at the root

38
00:04:35,916 --> 00:04:38,500
of the rogue syndrome
that has engulfed Tokyo.

39
00:04:38,583 --> 00:04:40,916
Rogue Boomers are therefore
the result of an orig--

40
