- ( object crashing ) 
- AH!

42
00:04:53,125 --> 00:04:54,375
OH, IT'S YOU.

43
00:04:54,458 --> 00:04:56,500
YOU SCARED THE HECK OUT OF ME.

44
00:04:56,583 --> 00:04:58,625
- WHOA, SO YOU'RE LEAVING TOO?

45
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:00,625
- YEAH, ONLY AN IDIOT
WOULD STAY HERE.

46
00:05:00,708 --> 00:05:03,166
I FIGURE I'LL CRASH AT MY
FOLKS' PLACE IN THE COUNTRY

47
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:04,541
UNTIL THINGS COOL DOWN.

48
00:05:04,625 --> 00:05:06,083
- MAXON'S ALREADY GONE.

49
