I NEVER THOUGHT THE GROUP
WOULD GO OUT LIKE THIS.

50
00:05:08,583 --> 00:05:11,041
- HMM.
WELL, WHAT ELSE CAN WE DO?

51
00:05:11,125 --> 00:05:13,541
SO HAVE YOU HEARD ANYTHING
FROM PRISS YET?

52
00:05:13,625 --> 00:05:17,375
- NO. AND I DON'T THINK SHE'S
BEEN BACK TO HER TRAILER EITHER.

53
00:05:17,458 --> 00:05:18,916
- YOU THINK--
- HMM.

54
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,666
I PITY ANY BOOMER THAT TRIES
TO TAKE THAT LADY DOWN.

55
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:25,125
- HA!
AND AIN'T THAT THE TRUTH?

56
00:05:25,208 --> 00:05:29,291
- BESIDES, SHE PROMISED US
A WORLD TOUR, REMEMBER?

57
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,916
- ( bird twittering )

58
